  "instructions": [
    "1. Preheat grill to medium-high heat.",
    "2. Cut the tofu into 1-inch cubes.",
    "3. In a small bowl, mix together Croatian seasoning, smoked paprika, salt, and pepper.",
    "4. Add the cubed tofu to the bowl and toss to coat with the spice mixture.",
    "5. Thread the tofu, crispy bacon, and garlic onto the skewers.",
    "6. Brush the skewers with olive oil and season with salt and pepper.",
    "7. Grill the skewers for 8-10 minutes, turning occasionally, until the tofu is golden brown and crispy.",
    "8. Serve hot with a squeeze of lemon juice."
